metadata.name: Aurum Priestess
metadata.description:
The Aurum Priestess is a powerful ritual leader; the divine host of the sun goddess, the bridge that connects both seen and unseen worlds.

"Aurum Priestess - Possessed" 2022, Robin Har
 
1/1 edition variation of Polygon multi-edition Golden Star World ArtDrop in collaboration with World of Women NFT.
